{"tid":1524393,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［無力感］曾經對黑警抱有一絲希望","createTime":"2019-08-31T17:08:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T17:42:42.000Z","uid":271820,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"f6a30d53cbf81779ec24580c72c2127cbb86409f","tid":1524393,"uid":271820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:08:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">以前會FF「如果全部警察都係幫市民，場運動一早贏咗啦」<br />\n721之後曾經期望過黑警會醒覺，棄暗投明<br />\n<br />\n而家發現根本冇可能<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n原來佢地唔係搵唔返良知</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">而係佢地根本冇良知，點都唔會搵得返</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">721<br />\n831</span></span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">呢一刻真係好無力感，眼見社會黑暗面一一曝光、顛倒是非；前線手足不斷被打被捕，但仲係乜訴求都爭取唔到，究竟我地仲可以做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n#五大訴求缺一不可<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8HtdQAi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8HtdQAi.jpg&h=bd65b20f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2a0zz1Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2a0zz1Y.jpg&h=568f2244&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"324d6249e0cfc6d5f07f879cbc971ac32c7802a7","tid":1524393,"uid":248384,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:11:15.000Z","msg":"是時候長大了 少年"},{"pid":"8185adb695eaf0cd63143c2a594dc1e857425ae1","tid":1524393,"uid":78570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:13:32.000Z","msg":"等美國開會阿<br />\n睇下D高官點比美國清算阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8f4fa163762d2d5c77a812eb0b1e599ce897f17","tid":1524393,"uid":62270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:13:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;